  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is the multi-center, open and cross-sectional study of RA remission in Asia
      Pacific region. The objectives is to explore remission rate of RA patients in different
      countries in the Asian-Pacific area using different criteria of remission (DAS28, CDAI, SDAI,
      ACR/EULA remission criteria, RAPID3 and Clin28) and investigate the associated factors of
      remission in RA patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
